local runService = game:GetService("RunService")
local character = script.Parent local humanoid = character:WaitForChild("Humanoid")
function updateBobbleEffect() local currentTime = tick() if character:WaitForChild("Head").LocalTransparencyModifier > 0.7 then if humanoid.MoveDirection.Magnitude > 0 then local bobbleX = math.cos(currentTime * humanoid.WalkSpeed/2) * .35 local bobbleY = math.abs(math.sin(currentTime * humanoid.WalkSpeed/2)) * .35
local bobble = Vector3.new(bobbleX, bobbleY, 0)
humanoid.CameraOffset = humanoid.CameraOffset:lerp(bobble, .25) else humanoid.CameraOffset = humanoid.CameraOffset * .75 end end end
runService.RenderStepped:Connect(updateBobbleEffect)
